 1992-15291992-07-150HON. ANDRE,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Honourable Harvie Andre of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Peter Alfred Gordon Cameron, Toronto, Ontario, in the place of Daniel J. Scanlan, whose term has expired; and Judith Marlane Romanchuk, Calgary, Alberta, in the place of Anne Chippendale, whose term has expired)
